## Prototype (Phase 1)

For Phase 1, we are demonstrating the system using a conceptual prototype.

This includes:
- User onboarding flow
- Weekly plan selection
- Real-time monitoring (weather and AQI)
- Trigger detection (e.g., AQI > 350)
- Automatic payout simulation

A visual UI prototype (Figma) will be added in the next phase to demonstrate the user flow more clearly.
